(0) READ-ITEM A B
(1) COMPARE A(I) TO B(J) ; IF GREATER GO TO OPERATION 5 ; OTHERWISE GO TO OPERATION 2
(2) STORE A(I) IN TEMP
(3) STORE B(J) IN A(I)
(4) STORE TEMP IN B(J) ; GO TO OPERATION 1
(5) WRITE-ITEM SORTED
(6) STOP
; Shell sort: generalization of insertion sort with gap sequence
; Input array: 64 34 25 12 22 11 90
; Process: gap=3, insertion sort, gap=1, insertion sort
; Output: 11 12 22 25 34 64 90
